Subject: report on permission change activity not updating
Description: found activity change report not updating
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue

report on permission change activity not updating

found activity change report not updating

Cause

No Root Cause


Resolution

Since the change was made at the top level in AD that change was reported in the ADI scan but not the FSAA system scan. We determined that this functions as expected and a change would need to be made at the file share level to report on file permission changes.
